data.title: Jack Dann on LinkedIn: When we say UK coverage, we mean it. Absolutely beautiful views today…
data.meta_description:
When we say UK coverage, we mean it. 

Absolutely beautiful views today working in Peterhead. Not looking forward to the drive home tomorrow, plenty of coffee…
